"Grylli helps you schedule messages, emails, and reminders that are sent "
"automatically if you fail to check in on time."
msgstr ""
"Mae Grylli yn eich helpu chi i amserlennu negeseuon, e-byst, ac atgoffa sy'n"
" cael eu anfon yn awtomatig os byddwch yn methu â gwirio mewn ar amser."

#: app/templates/help_partial.html:11
msgid ""
"It supports multiple delivery methods, user-level SMTP, rich scheduling, and"
" secure data handling."
msgstr ""
"Mae’n cefnogi sawl dull danfon, SMTP lefel defnyddiwr, amserlennu cyfoethog,"
" a thrin data diogel."

